00:04:09.439 --> 00:04:10.898
Well, in order for a constant value

00:04:10.898 --> 00:04:13.146
to be equal to a coefficient times x

00:04:13.146 --> 00:04:14.550
plus some other constant value

00:04:14.055 --> 00:04:17.803
the coefficient on X
must be equal to zero.

00:04:18.538 --> 00:04:20.302
Another way to think about it is,

00:04:20.302 --> 00:04:21.885
this should be,

