00:04:59.459 --> 00:05:02.454
So we figured out what m is.

00:05:02.454 --> 00:05:04.832
Then we could use that information,

00:05:04.832 --> 00:05:06.444
because we know that,

00:05:07.214 --> 00:05:10.651
we know that m is equal to,

00:05:10.651 --> 00:05:13.652
is equal to 3b minus 5.

00:05:14.168 --> 00:05:19.168
m is 2/3, so we get 2/3
is equal to 3b minus 5.

00:05:19.892 --> 00:05:21.653
We could add 5 to both sides,

00:05:21.653 --> 00:05:25.529
which is the same thing as
adding 15/3 to both sides.

00:05:26.308 --> 00:05:27.323
Is that, did I do that right?

00:05:27.458 --> 00:05:28.917
Yeah, adding 5 to both sides

00:05:28.917 --> 00:05:31.203
