adding 15/3 to both sides.

00:05:31.203 --> 00:05:32.196
So let's do that.

00:05:32.196 --> 00:05:37.196
15/3 plus 15/3, these cancel out.

00:05:38.069 --> 00:05:39.184
That's just 5 right over there.

00:05:39.184 --> 00:05:41.501
On the left-hand side we have

00:05:41.501 --> 00:05:46.262
